ound quality and maintainability. Instruments are available for sale to students, from beginner to professional grade. Click on links below for descriptions of musical instruments.</div>', 'Instruction', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '69-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-07-03 12:33:16', '2017-07-03 12:33:16', '', 69, 'http://vva.lo/index.php/2017/07/03/69-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
